      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit boasts a crisp 8,000 RPM redline and responsive individual throttle bodies. The chassis has been vetted with rear subframe reinforcement already completed, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, optimizing variable valve timing and valvetrain harmonics. Riding on a well-damped suspension with refreshed bushings, this M3 offers the tactile feedback and analog engagement enthusiasts crave. A driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
